jaroor aunl saab, lekin aunl raati hi kun, kilai ki din ma time ni mil sakano kasikai.
are theek chhe, raati hi kun aaye, lekin aaye jaroor.
din ma dukaan bhi dekhni to chhe, yo to paili duty chhe.
