chalo, pooj sampann hai ge. aab tum pranam kari ber teen baar parikrama kari lya, hath jodi ber.
hai ge parikrama puri. aab charanamrit lyo aur nan-tinan ke bhi bulao.
lyo jajman, pooj-paath hai go sampann.
yo thaila ma mi le prasad bhi, aashirwad bhi dhari halyo.
yo ghanti ke aab mandir ma kahin bandhi dya.
jai ho isht, inar bhal kariya. pariwar ma dhan-dhanya, sukh-shanti banaye rakhiya.
tumari kirpa le inar pooj-paath sampann hai go. jai ho bhagwan, jai ho gol jyu.
yo hamar taraf bati nanhi si dakshina swikaar kara, thodi-baut jatuk bhi chhe.
hamar jaste hi to chha aapn, jo time-betime kaam oonan.
are jajman, jo di dela, we lhi lyunl.
yek phikar ni kara.
dabal ki chhe, aadmik prem sabban bati thul cheej chhe.
tum ituk bharos le aunchha myar paas, yaso kuch ni bho yan.
tum aab hamar ghar kai jast hai gya chha.
tumar bhal hon chae.
sabban ke den waal yo hi parmeshwar chhan, inar hi aasro hamar bhi chhe.
ham to inar sewak chha.
hitanu pai aab, pandit jyu. phir kabhai darshan karula. ham to ooni raunu yan.
ho ho, kilai ni. aiya, phir aiya. aashirwad.
bhai saab, cha-paani chhe ki tumar yan?
are, coffee ko pyon? thul aadmiyan ki cheej chhe yo to. ham dwi janan lhi to cha hi banaye, jara badiya si.
ki baat ni, coffee ni, to cha hi sahi. kuch to piya.
gaahak jo kol, hamar kaam to we hi pyonak chhe.
cha kasi pyala, tapuk waali ki chini khitun?
tapuk waali? yaso ki kono chha aaj-bholak chini waala jamana ma?
baat to tum sahi kono chha dajyu, par pura uttarakhand ma ek myar hi dukaan chhe jath aelle bhi tapuk waali cha milan.
jara pi ber to dekha.
yaad karala tum bhi ki kasi cha pyai chhe lohaghat ma.
achchha. tareef to badi karano chha ho apan tapuk waali chaak. to lyao, tapuk waali hi cha pyai dya hamke bhi.
ki khanak bhi dyun tab tak?
aaluk gutuk chhan, pakodi chhe. cha banne tab tak.
di dya kuch bhi. gutuk taaja chhan to gutuk hi di dya, par khatayi khit ber dya bhai, aur bhuti mirch bhi.
yo lyo aaloo k gutuk aur special bhangak khatayi. khai ber yaad karala ki kahin aaloo k gutuk khaye chha.
wah-wah dada! tumal jibad ma swad jagai di. aur dya to gutuk. badi jordar hai rain sanchi ma.
tab hi to kono chhyu mi, yaad karala.
jhooth thodi kono chhyu.
aur khao jamai ber. cha bhi tayar chhe, dyun?
ho, di dya, lyao. jara ek gilaas paani bhi pyai dya, mirch badi lagi ge.
tapuk kaik lagola? gudak, misrik ki gattak?
tum to ajib naam lino chha tapukak. to yo gatt ki hunchh?
ham le to na kabhai sunyo, na khayo. dekhao to.
tab tum aaj gattak tapuk lagai ber hi cha piya. chaniyak cha famous chhe pura lohaghat ma.
achchha, to chani da chha tum. chalo, tumar naam bhi pato lagi go. dusr ke bhi batunl ki chanida wath cha jaroor pi ber dekhiya.
yaar, yasi cha wakai kahin ni pyai aaj tak.
namaskar ho dinesh, ki haal-chaal chhan, ki nai-taaji?
ki honi yaar nai-taaji, wesi hi chhe puran.
kilai, mi le suni ki chyalak byo thairai halyo.
haan, thair to go, par aelle taareekh tay ni bhai.
tab yaar kilai kono chha ki nai-taaji kuch ni hai rai? yo hi to taaji baat chhe.
are, taareekh pakki hai jaani tab hi to hunni nai-taaji, nai? aelle to baat hawa ma chhe yaar.
are, jab byo pakka hai go, wath taareekh bhi pakki hai jaali bhai.
we hi to dikat chhe. taareekh pakki hai jaani to phir pachason intejam bhi karan padanan yaar, unma time lagan.
gaun ma shaharak jaso ni hono, yith sabbai intejam karan padan.
are, aaj-bhol to ganth ma note hon chae yaar. intejam to mukh le hi hai jaanchh sab. banquet hall waal se ko, bas sabbai tayar. aadmike phikar karanak jarurat hi ni. kas?
chahe ki bhi ho, daud-bhaag to karan hi padan.
card chhapan padanan, lightak intejam bhi karan padan, gharak sauda-patta bhi kharidan padan. banquet hall waalanak to rate aasman ma chhan.
myar man ma to ghar bati karanak vichaar auno yaar. tu bata, kas theek raulo?
tyar baat suni ber myar dimaag ma ek idea aai go, batun?
bata, bata, ki idea aai tyar dalidri khopadi ma?
kilai re myar khopadike dalidri kono chhe? bees saal director rahyu sarkari vibhaag ma.
ki samajhe rakho make?
pachason nai-nai yojana mi le vibhaag ma chalai, jwe le vibhaag ke faida bho.
are dalidri chhe, jab wema yo idea ni auno ki yaar hita, ghar najik chhe, ghar hiti ber bojuk hathak ek ghutuk cha pi aala.
kath dharale ituk dabal, sharam kar.
are tyar lhi gharak dwar band hai rain ki re?
a, jab man karo tyar cha pyonak.
gharwaali tyar boju chhe, we to tyar oon ma khush hai jaali.
aab kai di to ni lijanu tuke apan dagad ghar.
ni lija, myar paas khut ni chhan ki? mi khud hi jaunl, aur jaunl ki, jaano chhu. tu ooni raye myar pachadi-pachadi.
hita pai agadi-agadi. are ruk yaar ruk, mi to bhuli geyu, tyar boju le ek packet cha k mangai rakhyo chho. make yaad hi ni chho.
mi ithe thado chhu.
e motor saikil, gaadi rok. ith laga kinare. license lye aur kagaj bhi dekha.
dajyu, ki galti hai ge mi bati? mi to theek hi chalano chhu apan side ma.
theek ni chalano tu. bina helmet gaadi chalono chhe.
pato ni chhe ki bina helmetak gaadi chalaun jurm chhe? kath runchhe tu?
dekhi lya kaagaj aur license dajyu, pura chhan sab.
achchha, pahadi chhe tu. kathak ran waal chhe?
dajyu, mi majkhali ma runu. aapn bhi pahadak hi chha ki?
ho, mi bhi pahadak hi chhu. hamar ghar jainoli chhe, ranikhet se pail.
phir to tum hamar ilaakak hi bhaye.
dada, asal ma mi haldwani motor saikil li ber paili ber auno chhu.
company ma service karan chhe yek, tab yeke li ber oon padyo.
tuke pato ni chho ki ith aaj-bhol badi sakhti hai rai?
bina helmet pair ber motor saikil chalaun ma chaalaan hai jaano.
koi riyayat ni hunne, kaske dagad bhi ni.
helmet to bado jaruri hai go aab ith.
par dajyu, sanchi kono chhu, make bilkul bhi pato ni chho ki helmet pairan jaruri hai go ith.
ranikhetak gaun ma wath to yasi koi checking ni hunni.
na wath yasa kanoonak koi jaankari chhe.
we jo karala aab. unke sanchi baat batai de aur maafi mangi lye.
mi bhi kuch kai dinu.
sir, yo chyal ranikhet bati gaadi li ber ith paili ber auno.
yeke pato ni chho ki ith helmet pairan jaruri chhe.
ranikhet ma to koi ni puchan, yek lhi wesi hi ith bhi aai go.
achchha, tuke pato ni chho ki ith aab helmet pairan jaruri hai go?
bina helmetak sidhe chalaan chhe.
sir, make pato huno to mi yasi galti kilai karanu?
make wakai pato ni chho. yo ber maaf kari dya.
chal, yo ber to tuke maaf karano chhu, we bhi yek lhi ki tu paili ber pahad bati haldwani auno chhe.
par maafi tab milali jab tu paili helmet kharidale aur aelle hi pair lele.
ja ho paan singh, yeke helmet waalak dukaan dekhai de.
hita, paar we saamne dukaan chhe ek. dabal chhan ki ni helmetak lhi tyar paas?
tum raun dya dajyu, mi jai ber khud kharid lyunl.
khaali kilai takleef karachha? make pato chhe dukaan.
dajyu, ek helmet di dya bhal so. katukak chhe?
chaar sau rupyak. theek chhe, yo lyo chaar sau rupya.
sir, yo dekha, aab mi le helmet kharidi ber pairi bhi halyo. aab to theek chhe.
ho, aab theek chhe.
chal, yo ber tuke pato ni chho, yek lhi maaf kari di mi le.
pachadi phir bina helmet pair ber ni dekhine chae make.
natar sidhe chaalaan kari dyunl. chal, bhaag ith bati aab.
theek chhe. aab ranikhet jai ber wath bhi sabban ke batai diye ki ith helmet pairan jaroori chhe.
sir, mi sabban ke batunl helmetak baare ma.
namaskar pandey jyoo.
namaskar ho harish bhai.
aur kas chha haal-chaal? ki nai-taaji chhe?
theek hi chhu yaar. 'saun sukho na bhado haro', sab ek hi jaso chhe.
wesi hi chhe yaar, phursat hi ni milan naukri bati.
baat to tum sahi kono chha.
tumar hi paas ayun. katuk din bati darshan hi ni hunain chho tumara.
sochan to mi bhi lagi rau chhyu yaar ki tyar paas aun kai ber, tu hi ai gachhe.
ek hi baat chhe, bhalai mi aun ya tum aao.
bhet hon se matlab chho, we hai go.
aao pai, aao bhiter, bhiter baitha. are charu, jara paani lye to.
le yaar, paani to pi paili. garmiyak din chhan, pyaas lagi rai holi.
ho chyala, paani pila paili. fridge k to ni chhe nee?
bas hai go chyala. jara yo pankha jor le chala de yaar.
are charu, jara apan ija se cha banan ke kə. aur suna ho, kas chha?
asal ma tum se ek raay lhin chhe make, pandey jyu, kilai ki tum thul chha.
are thul hon se ki ni, agar myar samajh ma aali baat to jaroor sahi-sahi batunl.
tum mansi k girish jyoo ke to jannana hi chha, unar chelik baare ma puchan chho.
kun girish? rebadhar jyoo k chyal? ho, unar pariwar ke bhale kari jannu.
are yaar, unar cheli basanti to laakhan ma ek chhe. sun samajh weke, sun!
wekai lhi puchan chho make. apan thul chyal chandan k lhi. kasi raali we?
are, aankh band kari ber lyao weke apan ghar. tum bhi ki yaad karala myar raay.
bas ituk hi raay jannan chho tumar, kilai ki tumke unar baare ma sabbai maalum chhe.
kab baat karano chha unse? jaldi kara, kahin haath bati muki ge to chyete raula.
are, ham ki karula. tum dagad hitala aur tum hi baat pakki karala, bas.
to bata, kab hitan chhe? tayyari bhi to karan padali unar wath jaanak.
pai bhol hi hitanu. gaadi chhe hi apan paas, chandan ke bhi lhi jaunu, dekh lyolo we bhi.
theek chhe, bhol hi hitanu. mi tayar raunl. bhyan hi nikal junla thanda-thanda ma, kas?
theek chhe, pakka rai. mi bhol bhyan ai junl gaadi li ber ith. aab hitanu.
namaskar ho ramesh.
yasi hi yaar, jara ek nanho kaam chho tyar se. karale to batun.
tyar karan layak hi chhe yaar, tab hi to tyar paas ayun. natar kilai unu?
hajaar rupyak ki jaroorat padi ge tuke aaj, jyek lhi myar paas oon padyo?
ki batun yaar, yo mainak tankhwa aelle tak ni mili, tab mushkil aai ge.
ki mushkil aai ge, bata to sahi, hal kari jaali wek.
yaar, makan-malik ke kiraya den chhe. weke jaroorat padi ge holi dabalan ki.
achchha, to yo chakkar chhe. ki baat ni, tu hajaar rupya lija aur weke di de.
tyar badi meharbani bhai, jo twe le myar kaam chalai di, natar pareshani hai jaani.
yema meharbanik ki baat? dosti ma ek-dusrak kaam oon chae hamke.
haan, we baat to chhe. phir bhi twe le sahara di, yek lhi kai mi le meharbani.
le pakad hajaar rupya, aur chae to aur lija. chinta ni kariye jab tak mi chhu.
dhanyavaad bhai. mi teen-chaar din baad aunl, tab dyunl tuke wapas. hitanu aab.
driver saab, kath tak jaane tumari gaadi?
yo to garud tak jaali. tumke kath jaan chhe?
aelle thodi der ma ranikhet bati aali gwaldam jaanak gaadi.
katuk der baad aali we? jagah mil jaali wema?
aadho ghanta baad. wema jai sakachha aaraam le, jagah bhi mil jaali.
ticket gaadi ma hi milalo ki?
ni, ni, ticket to bhiter counter bati lhin padal tumke.
katukak holo ticket ith bati gwaldam jaanak, batai dela?
assi rupya laganan ek sawarik ith bati.
dhanyavaad ho driver saab, tum le make bhale kari batai di.
ki baat ni, yo to hamar kaam hi chhe, sawari ke sahi batanak.
bhai saab, ek gilaas cha banai dela jaldi?
kath ituk jaldi hai rai? cha banan ma jara time to lagan hi chhe.
gwaldam jaan chhe mi le, dada. agar ranikhet waali gaadi chhut jaali to kasi jaunl?
chinta ni kara, driver bhi ith cha pi ber hi jaanchh. tum aaraam le cha piya.
tab theek chhe. aab aaraam le cha pi sakun. biskut bhi dya, bhook lagi rai.
biskut to khatam hai rain, pakodi khai lya. garam kari dinu, badiya pakodi chhan.
theek chhe, pakodi hi di dya. thodi khatayi bhi khita. cha jara bhali banaya.
chaak lhi ni kau, myar dukaanak cha ith mashahoor chhe. pyala to yaad karala.
aai ge ho gaadi, mi hitanu aur gaadi ma baithanu. tumar dhanyavaad.
doctor saab, namaskar.
doctor saab, teen din bati jarak maare haalat kharab chhe.
aang-peed badi jyaada hai ge, bhook bilkul ni chhe.
khwar ma peed bhi hai rai, sardi le naak bagane. pareshaan hai geyu.
bukhar napayo tum le? paili compounder se bukhar napai lyo, tab dawai lekhunl.
compounder saab, jara myar bukhaar naapi dya to.
doctor saab, ek sau teen chhe aelle.
khaan-pin ma ki lhi chho teen-chaar din pail, yo bhi make batao, tab hi sahi andaj aai sakal.
khaan-pin to gharak hi chho saab, par chaar din pail pyaas lagi rai chhe to ek fridge k thandi coca-cola pi di doston dagad.
bas wekai dusr din bati bukhaar aai go.
theek kai doctor saab, aapn le. aab bati mi kabhai thandi cheejan ke haath ni lagunl.
yele hi myar haalat kharab kari.
namaskar saab, aab hitanu. compounder saab, yo parchik dawai di dya, aur kasi lhin chhe, we bhi batai dya.
yo dwi-dwi goli khani chhan din ma teen ber garam paani dagad.
yo ek goli bhyan naashta kare ber, aur din ma chaar ber yo pyonak dawai ek dhakkan garam paani ma milai ber pi lya.
sau rupya dekhanak aur assi rupya dawaik. ek sau assi rupya di dya.
yo lyo compounder saab, paanch sau rupyak note chhu.
are bhai, tuta dabal dya. ith tuta dabal ni chhan myar paas. bhyan-bhyan khula dabal ni hunan.
theek chhe, mi bhyar bati tudai lyon, aelle dinul tumke. myar paas bhi tuta ni chhan.
ho ho, ki baat ni. tudai lyao, aaj-bhol badi pareshani chhe tuta dabalan ki.
yo lyo compounder saab, ek sau assi rupya. tudai lyayun paanch sauk note. dhanyavaad aapn ke.
aao dajyu, kath jaan chhe? gaadi tayar chhe.
jaan to bhai almora chho. tum jaano chha ki?
dabal katuk leno chha? yo bhi to batao paili.
are baki ki len, bas dwi sau rupya matra.
dwi sau badi jyaada chhan yaar, dedh sau lyo.
tel mahango hai go dajyu, ki karan. yek lhi dwi sau hai go kiraya.
sabbai ituk hi dinan, puchhi lyo.
theek chhe bhai, jab sabbai dwi sau hi dinan to dyunl mi bhi. par paili batao, kath baithun, agadi ki pachadi?
jath tumari ichchha chhe. agadi bhi khaali chhe, pachadi bhi khaali chhe.
jath bhal lagan, wath baitha aaraam le.
waso chhe to phir agadi hi baithanu pai, kilai ki agadi theek runchh. bhal-bhal seen dekhinan.
aaraam le baitha agadi, par dajyu, seen dekhan ma hari ni jaiya. myar matlab, suti ni jaiya.
ni ho, kilai situl agadi baithi ber? ulto tumke hi dekhano raunl ki tumke need to ni aane.
tum to samjhdar lagana chha. yo bag make di dya, pachadi diggi ma dhari dinu, ith asaj holi.
dhari dya pachadi, par jara aaraam le dhariya.
kilai, ki chhe yema aaraam le dharanak layak?
are yaar, mithai dhari rakhi. pachak jaali, tab kono chhu.
aab hita phata-phat, seat puri hai gein. bhook bhi lagane, garampani ma ruki ber khaan-pin kari jaal.
hitanu dajyu. gaadi k mamlo chhe, sabbai cheej dekhan padan, agadik pahadak safar chhe.
