gaun me barkhaatak taiyari kasi chalan lagi
sab apan chhan sudharan aur kath jama karan me lagi raye
meke sanj bakhat u kath k dhuek baas bado chet auni
mele yahan ek nawo sangi banai we punjab bati chhan
yo bhal chha par u meri jasi ni hwe sakani
tuar jaso koi ni hwe sakan tu mero nanpanak sangi chha
tu hamar u chyudk jangal dagadi gupat thaan par geyi kya
me bhyal geyun chhu u tuar bina katuk suno lagan chho
tu wahan thodi der baithi
hao aur mele hamar sari puni baat chet kari
mera sasural wala agla saal gaun aunak bichar kran rayen
sachi yo to bado bhal chha ham unar dil kholi ber swagat karul
ham unke sab ghumaul unke hamar gaun bado pasand aal
tumar dagad batulai ber meke aso lagan ro jaso ki me gaun me hi chhu
aur tumar dagad batulai ber meke aso lagan ro jaso ki tu kabh geyi hi ni
hamar dosti yo doori ke sanch mehsus ni hune dyali
sada kaaj mera sangi
u puno aam ko ped abhil tak chha kya
meke uk khata kaancha aam bado chet aani
meke yahan pinjare me band chidi jaso lagan ro
par yo pinjro to son ko chha ni ho kya
chutt to sona bati bhi mehengi chha sangi
me samjhan chhu par tuke yo pinjre ke hi apun ghar banan padal
mero nano bhai padhai me kaso kran ro
u tuar jaan baad bado baanth hwe go u kweek ni sunano
we dagad batulaiya we tuar sunanchha use kwa ki man lagai ber padho
bas apan aankhi munj dya me tuar dagadi hasan milul
tuke sada pato hunchha ki meke kasike bhal lagan chahano
sangi we hi kaam lai to hunchhan
shahare meke ek cheej sikhai apan gaunak kimat
kweek bhi cheejak kimat uke harayan baad hi pato chalni
sanch chha mele yo sab cheejon ke sasto samjhi liyo
pachhtawa na kara bas cheton ke sanjoya
dekhi kya bhyal raat bati hyun padan lagi go
hao puro gaun hyun le dhap dhap hwe go katuk bhal dikhano
bhal to chha par ab janjal shuru hol baat ghat sab band hwe jaal
aur jaad bhi bado chha mera haath khut abhil bati hi thithuran lag geyi
aaj gham katuk karak chha jaso ki chhal jalai dyali
hao aur dhara naula bhi sukhana lagi geyi ab paani ko kaal padal
hamke apan sab gagri balti bhari leni chahani jab tak thodo paani chha
me wele hi abhil dhara taraf jan chhu
dui din bati lagatar paani padan ro ghar ki diwalon me seel aani lagi
meri chhan chunan lagi mele tale ek balti rakhi chha
yo chaumas bado janjal walo chha
par charai taraf hariyaali dekha aankhi ke katuk thandak milani
yo saal badon fasal bado bhal hwe rakhi
hao daana mota chhan ritu anukul chhe
ab daain lagan aur anaj bhandar me rakhan ki mahinat shuru holi
u bhi thul kaam chha par bharyun bhandaar dekhan ko aanand hi alag chha
paar wala jangal me aag lagi chha dhun dikhano kya
hao bado thul lagan ro aas chha ki hawa uke yati taraf na lyao
garmi me yo hi sabse thul khatra chha ek chingaari aur puro pahad jali janchha
pirul jalan ki baas har taraf failan lagi
dangar bachh ab charna lai bahar kasike jaalan
hamke unke jama kari rakhi sukhi ghas khilani padali
yo hyun bado lamo aur kathin honu
meke barkhaat baad ko saaf neel aakash bado bhal laganchha
hao aur himal katuk saaf dikhano ke najaro chha
yo pahadan me rahan kaaj sabse bhal ritu chha
baat paani le katuk chikni hwe ge me lagbhag padi geyun
sambhali ber hida pahaad khisan ko dar bhi chha
hyun me gham peeth par katuk bhal laganchha
hao man karno ki bas din bhar aangan me hi baithi raun
par ghar ko katuk kaam karno chha
garmi ki hawa katuk sukhi aur taati chha yeke loo kunechan
aso lagan ro jaso ki chul k agadi baitha chhan
feri feri tiras lagani
hao pyoli aur burans katuk bhal dikhan chhan
yo phool dei jaso tyoharon ki ritu chha
puro vatavaran aanandmay lagan ro
hyun ki raat katan ni katni
aur katuk thandi bina rajai k sutan asambhav chha
me to dui rajai lino tabi bhi jaad lagan ro
hamar pahadan ko jaad bado kaad hunchha
ab hyun ki fasal kaaj gehun bunan ko bakhat hwe go
hao hamke khet tayar kar lena chahani pail hi ki jameen jaad le kaad hwe jao
yo kheti ko chakkar kabh ni rukano ritu baad ritu
yahi hamar jyun chha daaju yahi hamar kaam chha
barkhaat me bado keeda makoda aur jonk hwe janchhan
hao ghas me hidte bakhat bado sambhali ber rahan padan
bhyal mera khut me ek jonk lagi geyi
we bado kharab hunchhin we ragat chusi linchhin
naun natin ki garmi ki chuttiyan shuru hwe geyi
aur we puro din ghaad me khelte raalan
yo unar majo karan ko bakhat chha khelan diya unke
nalak paani jami go ab ke karu
hamke dhara par jaber barf todi ber paani lyaun padal
karak hyun me yo ek thul dikkat chha
jyun bado kathin hwe janchha
fasal katne baad khet katuk khali aur udas dikhan chhan
hao par unke bhi aaram chahanchha hamar jaso hi
ab we agli fasal kaaj pheri jodi jaalan
jyun aur kaam ko chakkar chalte rano
sanch chha we barkhaat ki raaton k raja chhan
garmi ki ropai bati pail hamke khetan bati ghas-pat saaf karni chha
hao taati gham me yo bado mahinat ko kaam chha
par agar ni karul to ghas-pat bali ke nasan kari dyala
kheti-pati to khali karak mahinat hi chha
hyun me kapad kai din tak ni sukhana
hao kikaji ki gham ni huno unme seelak baas aani lag janchha
hamke unke chul k dagad sukhan padan
sambhali ber ni to we aag pakdi sakanchhan
mele aaj paani baad indradhanush dekhi
yo bado shubh sagun mani janchha
rang katuk chatak aur bhal chhayi
kudrat apan rup kai rakam le dikhano
ab din nana huni lagi geyi badon aai go
hao aur sanj thandi huni lagi
yo saal ko mero sab bati bhal bakhat chha
mero bhi hawa taaji aur nirmal lagani
sukha hyun me mera haath-khut faati janchhan
unpar sutan bati pail ghyu lagaya ule bado faida hunchha
puna jatan hi sab bati bhal hunchhan
barkhaat me ghaad pura ufan par hunchha
uk najik janu khatarnak chha dhaar bado tej hunchha
pul bhi kabh kabh paani me dubi janchha
aur fir hamar gaun ki paar taraf lai aan-jaan band hwe janchha
har rituk apan rup chha aur apan janjal
yo ekdam sanch chha yahi to pahadak dastoor chha
hame yo sab dagad rahan seekhi liyo chha
wele hi ham aatasila hunchhan
yo sagun chha ki basant panchami najik chha
basant rituk raunak hi alag hunchha
hao lamba thanda hyun baad yo ek nayi shuruat jaso laganchha
pattharak paani padan lago sab phool nasai jaalan
he bidhata yo to yo saal ko falad nasan kari dyalo
bemausam paani aur patthar bado nuksan karchhan
ek kisanak jyun sada rituk bharos hunchha
chala chyau chunan jaun we pail paani baad bhot uganchhan
meke pato chha kun wala todana meri aama le sikhayo chha
bhal tab chala unar saag bado swaadilo hunchha
me garmi ki dhul bati thaki geyi
har cheej bhuri dhul ki ek parat le dhaki janchha
kaash paani jaldi aai jao aur sab kuch saaf dhwe diyo
har koi chaumas ki baat dyekhan ro
mera nanpan me bado jada hyun padan chho
sanch chha ab hyun utlo kaad ni huno
rituk saara chakkar badali go
yo duniya me ek thul badlav ko sagun chha
badon ki raati sab bati bhal hunchhin
hao saaf aakash taron le bharyun hunchha
aso laganchha jaso ki tum bas haath badhai ber unke chhui sakala
tume asi raati shahar me ni milan
meke paani padan bati theek pail matik baas bado bhal laganchi
meke bhi u ek bado khaas sugandh chha
u batanchha ki garmi bati rahat milan wali chha
u kudrat ki ghoshna chha
yo kweer etuk bankal chha ki agadi ko manukh tak ni dikhano
yo hyun ki byanh pahadan me aam chha
aso lagan ro jaso ki baadal k bhitar hidan chhan
aajkal gham katuk jaldi dubano
hao hyun k din nana hunchhan
aur kaam katuk jada kaam siran bati pail din siri janchha
wele hi to hamke apan din jaldi shuru karno padan
chaumas ki pail jhad dagad bhyagulan le turran shuru kari diyo
yo barkhaat rituk sangeet chha
kuch logon ke yo pareshan karchha par meke bhal laganchha
ped par aadu dekha we garmi ki gham me pakan lagan
we yo saal bado meetha aur raswala holan
hamke unke chidiyon aur bandaron bati bachan padal
wehi to sabse thul chunauti chha
har ritu me alag rakamak karak mahinat chahani
ek kisan lai koi aaram ni
par apan mahinat le ugayo anaj khane me santosh milanchha
tufan bati pail ki hawa bado jorak aur daroni hunchha
hao aso laganchha jaso ki u chhan hi udai dyali
hamke sab dangar bachh bhitar lyana chahani
mele unke pail bati hi goth me baandhi diyo chha
hyun me aghinyak dagad baithiber katha sunanak majo hi alag chha
hao hamar bajyu katuk katha sunanan chhayi
ab kweek dagad bakhat hi ni sab apan phone me byast chhan
bakhat badali go daaju
badon me puro jangal jameen sukha paat le dhaki janchha
u bado bhal awaj hunchha
hao aso laganchha jaso kudrat koi geet ganan ro
dhaan k khet barkhaat me hari dari jaso dikhan chhan
u gaun ko sab bati bhal najaro hunchha
aur jab hawa chalanchha to we laharon jaso hilchan
bas uke dekhi ber hi jyu jumas janchha
lambi barkhaat baad gham katuk taato aur anmol laganchha
hao aso laganchha jaso ki jyun pheri aai go
ab ham jama hwe rakhiya saara kapad dhwe sakanchhan
aur seela anaj ke sukhai sakanchhan
wehi to sab bati bhal baat chha hamke saal bhar alag alag cheej khanak milchha
hyun me muli garmi me kakdi
kudrat le bado bhal sanjog banayee chha
hyun ki thandi hawa haddiyon me ghusni jasi laganchha
hao khaaskar byanh aur sanj bakhat
bina topi aur muffler k bahar nikalnu asambhav chha
mele to apan saara taata kapad pail bati hi nikali diyan
me darak mare raat bhar ni suti sakiyun
ham sab ke paani ki baltiyon dagad jaagi rahan padigo
aaj hyun ki gham bado kamjor lagani
hao umen jatti bhi taakat ni jaad kam ni huno
tab dangar bachh lai janjal pheri badhi jaal
hawa gungunan lagi garmi ko tufan auno walo chha
chala jhatke kapad taar bati bhitar lye aaun
aur jo anaj sukhan lai rakhi chha uke bhi uthan padal
yo bemausam paani sada galat bakhat par aunchha
mero bhi hamar ghar k mathi ko danda bado darono lagan ro
pichla saal wahan bati ek thul patthar ghiryo chho aas chha ki yo ber aso ke na ho
ham khali bhumiyal devta se binti kari sakanchhan wehi hamar rakshak chhan
paki gehun le khet sunahala hwe geyi ke bhal najaro chha
hao badon rituk apan hi raunak chha
ab bali lunan ki karak mahinat shuru holi
hawa me jalan ki baas auni najik me aag lagi kya
paar wali daandik pirul jangal chha yo ritu me yo aam baat chha
bado dukh laganchha katuk ped paudha aur jeev jantu mari janchhan
hyun k karan dangar bachh din bhar bhitar hi rakhan padan
aur goth saaf karanak kaam aur thul hwe janchha
hao unar ghas paani sab bhitar hi karno padan
hyun me janjal das guna badhi janchha
raat me teen ki chhan par paani ki awaj bado bhal laganchi
hao ule neend bhal auni
jab tak ki chhan chunan na lagi jao
hahaha tab wehi awaj chinta ko karan bani janchha
puro parivar dhaan ki katai me byast chha
hao yo ham kisanan kaaj saal ko sab bati byast bakhat chha
yek baad ham shaanti le diwali manai sakula
hao bhandaar bharyun hune par tyar aur aanandmay laganchha
yo saal pharsi bado thul hwe geyi
barkhaat bhal chhe maati ke puro paani milo
ab ham unar bada banala
mera mukh me to sochi ber hi paani aai go
garmi ki taap manukh ke katuk alsi aur sust banai dinchha
sanch chha koi bhi kaam karanak man ni karno
bas man karno ki thando paani piyun aur chhanv me suti jaun
me kai lagyi baat par chhipali geyun yo ritu me jameen bado seeli ra chha
tuke maar to ni lagi bado savadhan rahan padan
me bhal chhu bas thodi kharonch aai par mera kapad maila hwe geyi
yahi to barkhaatak janjal chha lagatar hilo aur seel
hyun pighalan baad pahad katuk saaf aur taaja dikhan chhan
hao jaso ki kudrat le unke nhalai diyo
aur pighalto hyun ko naun me badalanak awaj bado sangeetmay hunchha
har rituk apan khaas sangeet hunchha
dhaan ropanak bakhat aai go
hao chaumas lagan walo chha hamke khet tayar karna chhan
yo kammar todan walo kaam chha
par yo bado tyar bar ko bakhat bhi hunchha jab did bhuli geet gan ganchhin
badon ki gham jada karak ni huno bado bhal laganchha
hao yo bahar baithiber anaj saaf karan jaso kaam karan lai ekdam sahi chha
aur padosiyon dagad gap sap karan lai bhi
