hyun ki sabjiyan ugan lagi geyi muli palak
hyun ki saag paatak swaad hi alag hunchha
khaaskar apan khetak muli
we ek hi sang katuk meethi aur tej hunchhin
chaumas me baadal fatanak dar rano bado darono hunchha
hao ghaad minton me ufan par aai janchha
hamke yo ritu me sada satark rahan padan
pahadan me rahan himmat ki lagatar pariksha jaso chha
