par yo dangar bachh lai bhal chha unke khana lai dher mili jaal
har cheejak apan faida aur nuksan hunchha
yahi kudrat ko niyam chha
garmi me hawa pirul k lisa ki sugandh le bhari ra chha
meke u baas bado bhal laganchi u meke mera nanpan ki chet diwayinchha
bajar jan wali baat pahaad khisan le band hwe ge
ab uke saaf karan me kam se kam dui din lagal
hamar saari saag paat sadi jaali katuk nuksan hwe go
yo chaumas ki ek lagatar dikkat chha
bhari hyun padan baad bado ghanghor chupchap hwe janchha
hao aso laganchha jaso ki puri duniya suti geyi
aur khali pedan bati pighalto hyun ki tap tap awaj auni
yesle man ke bado sukun milanchha
hamke barkhaat me baat band huni bati pail noon tel jama kari lenu chahano
tum sanch kun chha teen mahina kaaj ham lagbhag duniya bati kati janchhan
yo tayari pahad me jyun bachana kaaj bado jaruri chha
yo sab hamke hamar bajyang le sikhayo chha
oho u bado swadilo hunchha mera kaaj bhi thodo rakhiya
