hao thandi ritu aur saaf raat k aakash dagad
diya andhyar pahadan k agadi aur bhal dikhanchhan
aso laganchha jaso ki tara jameen par utari aayi geyi
mungari paaki ge khet katai kaaj tayar chhan
yo rituk wehi to sab bati bhal baat chha
chaumas me ghar me har bakhat seelak baas auni
hao aur diwal chhun par thandi laganchhin
me seel dur karana lai chul me aghin jalai rakhan chhu
bas wehi ek jatan chha
hao we jyu ke garmi dinchan
jaad me taati roth dagad gud ghyu khanak majo hi alag chha
tumi to baat kari ber hi meri bhuk badhai di
jhadon par kilmudi paaki geyi
chala bhol byhan unke todan jaunla naun nati bado raji holan
par unar kaan bado paij hunchhan hamke sambhali ber rahan padal
ghaad barkhaat me risai rano
uke dekhano bhal bhi chha aur darono bhi
wehi to kudrat ko asli roop chha
badon ki fasal baad bya baraton ki ritu shuru hunchha
hao jab bhandaar bharyun hunchhan aur logon dagad paisa hunchha
yo charai taraf raji khushi aur tyar bar ko bakhat hunchha
sab bati manbhani ritu chha meri
yo garmi pichla saal bati jada lagani
pato ni aun walo saalon me ke hol
yo sab jangal katna karan chha ham keemat chukan rayan
me bhi bina kath k yahan hyun ni kati sakan
yo sab bati jaruri tayari chha
anaj kapad bati bhi jada jaruri
aaj raatak jun dekha badon k aakash me katuk saaf aur ujjal chha
hao aso laganchha jaso ki tum umen daag tak dekhi sakala
pahadan me purnimak raatak raunak alag hi hunchha
u tumar saari chinta bhulai dinchha
ghaadak paani ab barfak jaso thando chha
umen haath halanu tak kathin chha
aur hamke yo paani me kapad dhunan padan
hamar haath sunn hwe janchhan pahadi syani manik jyun saral ni
me garmi ki saag paatak achaar banan chhu hyun me khana kaaj
yo bhal bichar chha hyun me jada taaji sabjiyan ni hunin
yesi hi ham ek rituk swaad dusar ritu kaaj bachai rakhanchan
baadal garjanak awaj le mero jyu uchhali janchha
mero bhi me jhatke jaber dewalay me diyo jalai dinchhu
meri aama kunan chhi ki bhagwanak naam japan chahano
ule himmat milanchi
basantak pail phool khili geyi
ab naun nati phool dei tyar manala
we ghar ghar phool aur chaanwal lye ber jaalan
yo ek bhal parampara chha jo nayi rituk swagat karchha
barkhaat me ghar me makadik jaala katuk badhi janchhan
aur diwal seel le kaali hwe janchhin
ghar saaf karno yo ritu me ek lagatar kaam chha
hyun ki gham aalu k chips banan kaaj bhal hunchha
hao we bina jali ekdam bhal kari suki janchhan
aur fir ham unke saal bhar tali ber khai sakanchhan
hamar gaunak tarika hi sab bati bhal chhan
ek hi kamre me din bhar aghin jalai ber rahan le mero dam ghutano
par ke karu baharak jaad asahaniya chha
kaash yo hyun jaldi siri jao
dheeraj rakha sangi har ritu gujar janchha
badon ki thandi hawa me bas khet me ghumana ko man karno
hao peeth par gham aur hawa me halki thandak dagad
yo pura saal ki sab bati aaramdayak ritu chha
me tuar baat se puri tarah sehmat chhu
khataruwak tyar aai go ham aghin jalala
aur ham aghin me kakdi chadhala
hamar tyar bar rituon bati katuk gehra jude chhan
kaad jaad me byanhak kaam kaaj lai uthnu katuk kathin hunchha
sanch chha paani barfak jaso laganchha
aur haath kaam karana bati jawab di dinchan
par kaam to karno hi padan chahe jaad ho ya garmi
gham vitamin d kaaj bado bhal hunchha
hao khaaskar hyunak byanhak gham
wele hi hamar buda bajyang ghanton tak gham me baithen chhayi
unke bhal jyunak bhed pato chho
me badon ritu kaaj genda k phool ropan chhu
we diwali k aas paas bhal kari phulalan
aur ham unke pooja me prayog kari sakanchhan
phool tyaron ke aur bhi bhal banai dinchan
paani baad har taraf khalya hwe geyi
aur naun nati unme raji khushi uchhalan rayen
karan diya nanpan aso hi hon chahano
hao nischint aur maja le bharyun
pradhanak chunav pheri najik aai geyi
hao ab sab ummidwar haath jodi ber hamar dwaar par aalan
aur jeetan baad paanch saal tak gayab hwe janchhan
yo har berak katha chha daaju
tum yo ber bhot kuke dyala
me uke diunl jo hamar gaunak baat sahi karanak bachhan dyalo
bachhan to sab dinchan kaam koi ni karno
tabi bhi hamke kipar to bharos karno hi padan
bhyal raat ummidwar kamal aur paisa baatan chho
u bhot khareedanai kosis kran ro uk chakar me ni padan
ham kamal lye lyula par bhot layak manukh ke hi dyula
hamar bhot bikau ni
yo abhi walo pradhan le jatti bhi kaam ni kari
ule bas apan pet bhari schoolak diwal abhil tak tuti chha
yo ber hamke uke ni jeetan den
puro gaun we bati naraj chha
dui bhai chunav me ek dusarak khilaf thad chhan
yo rajneeti unar parivarik rishta kharab kari dyali
yo kursik lalach buri cheej chha
yo bhaiyon ke bairi banai dinchha
ummidwarak bhashan aaj bado joshilo chho
u kun chho ki u gaun me aspatal lyalo
ham yo bachhan bees saal bati sunan rayan
hao sab bhal kapad pairi ber bhot den janchhan
yo hamar kartavya chha aakhir me
we bhot kaaj gaun ke jaat paat k aadhar par baatan rayen
yo bado galat chha pradhan pura gaun kaaj hunchha
abhi wala pradhanak chyal bado ghamandi chha
u asi ghumanchha jaso ki u gaun ko rajkumar chha
babak takat wek muud par chadhi ge
yo ber gaun wala unke sabak sikhala
meke yo rajneeti samajh ni auni we sab ek jaso hunchhan
par bhot denu jaruri chha ni to galat manukh jeeti jaal
bhal me jaunl tumar hisab le kun bhal ummidwar chha
meke laganchha ki school k maasab bhal manukh chhan we padhya likhya aur imandar chhan
sarkare yo ber pradhanak seat syani maani kaaj rakhi di chha
yo bado bhal chha syani maani ke bhi mauka milan chahano
par unar log hi pichhyan bati raj chalala
tabi bhi yo ek shuruat chha cheejen haule haule badlali
bhyal dui ummidwaron k chelon beech thul jhagda hwe go
chunav k bakhat yo sada hunchha ule gaunak mahaul kharab hwe janchha
we ek dusare ke bhal buro kunan chhayi
yo bair ab saalon tak raal
tuar ummidwar ke kun chinha milo chha
uke ugto suraj ko chinha milo chha
aur hamar wala ke nal ko chinha milo chha
dekhla kweek suraj uganchha aur kweek nal paani dinchha
ummidwar hamar ghar aayo aur mera khut chhui
we chunav bati pail bado nyav hwe janchhan
aur jeetan baad we tume chhinan tak ni
yahi to rajneeti ko swabhav chha
me yo chunavi railiyon aur halla bati thaki geyi
unar gaadiyon le hamar saankad gaunak baata kharab kari di
unke bas apan bhotak chinta chha hamar janjalak ni
